com.camerontec.catalys.core.session

Class SessionOverseer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.catalys.util.configuration.AbstractConfigurable
      • com.camerontec.catalys.server.component.ComponentHelper
        • com.camerontec.catalys.core.session.SessionOverseer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IComponent, IHasAttributes, IConfigurable, IRegisterable

    public final class SessionOverseer
extends ComponentHelper
    Singleton object which periodically examines the usage of all started sessions in the Catalys Server in order to tune their performance.

    Currently, it:

    • Checks whether or not each session should flush its output stream after each write
    • Checks for stuck sessions and terminates their connections (if configured to)
    • Checks for time outs in unqueued mode and switches the session to queued mode
